name: Astrohouse: Glitch Phase
description: We all have seas of mind to swim in, seas of thought to drown in, seas of emotion to swallow, social seas to live 4 and in all of that 2 you, you need many lighthouses of love of truth, of beauty and joy to stay above water, and if you do that well, you will levitate through light and truth, beyond space-time, in the juices of mind.
